name: Face the Emptiness
description:
Can you face the Emptiness? We artists are always endangered fallen into, ultimately forced to fight through and overcome it.

Next entry in the Golden Loop Series feat. some good grooves! 
This one is a highly hypnotic flow in sync with the music.

Original work is rendered in 4k but due to the 100MB limit, I mint the 2k version for better quality in compression.
